<font color=teal>Muselu Wapama wa Yesu Kirixtu woolebiwa ni Matewuzhi</font>Makolo a Yesu<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?42.3.23-38">Luka 3.23-38</a>)Ala bi makolo a Yesu Kirixtu,<RF q=+>Kirixtumu ewogelo ya eGerego enatapulela Muthikitheliwi, Misiya, naari wi: oosakuliwa a Mulugu, oyene onaavulumuse athu. Moone teto verisikulu 16. namabaliwelamo a Davidi, mwaana a Abarahamu.
• Abarahamu ahimbala Ezaaki;• Ezaaki ahimbala Yakobo;• Yakobo ahimbala Zhuda ni addibile;
• Zhuda aali babe a Perezi ni Zera. (Mmeewa aali Tamari.)• Perezi aali babe a Heziromo;• Heziromo aali babe a Aramu;
• Aramu aali babe a Aminadabi;• Aminadabi aali babe a Naxoni;• Naxoni aali babe a Salimoni;
• Salimoni aali babe a Bowazi.• (Bowazi amaaye yaali Rahabi.)• Bowazi aali babe a Obeddi.• (Obeddi amaaye yaali Ruti.)• Obeddi aali babe a Zhesi;
• Zhesi aali babe a Kingi Davidi;• Davidi aali babe a Salomawu.• (Salomawu amaaye yahikala mwadha Uriya.)
• Salomawu aali babe a Robowamu;• Robowamu aali babe a Abiya;• Abiya aali babe a Aza;
• Aza aali babe a Zhosafati;• Zhosafati aali babe a Zhoramu;• Zhoramu aali babe a Uziya;
• Uziya aali babe a Zhotamu;• Zhotamu aali babe a Akaazi;• Akaazi aali babe a Ezekiya;
• Ezekiya aali babe a Manasesi;• Manasesi aali babe a Amoni;• Amoni aali babe a Zhosiya;
• Zhosiya aali babe a Zhekoniya ni addibile mudhidhi oyene wacedheliwiiwa oBabilooniya.<RF q=+>Moone Mamwene a Nabiili 24.14-15
• Vano vacedheliwiiwa oBabilooniya:• Zhekoniya aali babe a Salatiyeli;• Salatiyeli aali babe a Zorobabeli;
• Zorobabeli aali babe a Abiyudi;• Abiyudi aali babe a Eliyakimu;• Eliyakimu aali babe a Azori;
• Azori aali babe a Zadoki;• Zadoki aali babe a Akimu;• Akimu aali babe a Eliyudi;
• Eliyudi aali babe a Eleyazari;• Eleyazari aali babe a Matani;• Matani aali babe a Yakobo;
Mowinda wambeela wa Abarahamu ofiyedha wa Davidi yavirile anamabaliwelamo dila kumi ni nnayi, wambeela wa Davidi ofiyedha ocedheliwa oBabilooniya yavirile anamabaliwelamo dila kumi ni nnayi, wambeela mudhidhi woocedheliwa oBabilooniya ofiyedha obaliwa wa Kirixtu ole aroromelihiwe yavirile anamabaliwelamo dila kumi ni nnayi.
Obaliwa wa Yesu<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?42.2.1-7">Luka 2.1-7</a>)Obaliwa wa Yesu Kirixtu weereyile ayi: Mariya, maaye a Yesu, agaveviwe ni Zhuuze, ehinagone vamohi, ahifwanyeya aganna wari odheela mwa owodha wa Muneba Woweela.
