Onaagonjihe oneere waakela mareeliho alene. Vano ginaakale Mulugu aaye, oliye onaakale mwaana aaga.
Mbwenye owoova, oohuroromela, amagaadde, mapanga, anamararuwa, akwiri, anameebedha dhingamuthu ni anamaratha aatene yowaakela yeewa si nyaza enapaha ni munddo ni enxofere. Wula fu okwa wa nabiili”.
Zheruzalemi muxaAhidha mungero mwa atanu ni abiili anna mapusulano matanu ni meenddi yadhaalile milili mitanu ni miinddi dhoogomihedha. Owoga ni miyo, wiira: “Kadha, guwoonihe namateliwa, mwadha a Nibila”.
Gahihiddiwa ni Muneba Woweela, mungero ahigithukulela omwaangoni mulubale, wootaama. Vevale ahigooniha Zheruzalemi nluwa noweela nikitaga wa Mulugu odhulu,
nizherimelaga ni nthithimiho na Mulugu. Oozherimela wona nibwe nookwima, noorameya, wona zhaxipe, nowooneyela wona viiduru.
Nluwa ndde nahikalana cinga nuulubale, nootaama. Teto nahikalana milago kumi ni miinddi. Kadda mulago vookala mungero, milago ndo dhootopiwa ndina na malogo kumi ni meenddi na ahima a Ezarayeli.
Dhipaddi dhaatedhene nnayi wookala milago miraaru: Omakumelo wa nduwa miraaru, omadhowelo wa nduwa miraaru, omurogweni miraaru, omurubini miraaru.
Cinga na nluwa namagiwe vadhulu va mabwe malubale kumi ni meenddi. Mmabweni mule mwahilebiwa mandina kumi ni meenddi a arumiwi kumi ni abiili a Nibila.
Mungero ole awoga ni miyo ahikalana mpimo wa oro wi apimena nluwa, milago ni cinga.
Nluwa ndda nooligana dhipaddi dhannayidhene. Orambalala wiwa wooligana ni malapeloya. Mungero ole ahipima ni mpimo waaye, yaali makilomeeturu macikwi meenddi ni mazana meenddi . Orambalala wiwa ni malapeloya ni mataameloya wooligana.
Teto ahipima pida ya cinga, yaali meeturu makumi matanu ni nimohi ni matanu . Mungero ole ahipima ni mukalelo mmohive wapimana athu.
Cinga ndde namagiwe ni mabwe eneeriwa zhaxipe, nluwana namagiwe ni oro apamesesa wona viiduru.
Mabwe malubale a matibelelo a cinga na nluwa yahiwomihiwa ni mabwe ookwima a misawo-misawo. Nibwe nuulubale nowambeela nahiwomihiwa ni mabwe a zhaxipe, nibwe na nabiili nahiwomihiwa ni mabwe a safira, nibwe na neethaaru ni mabwe a kalisedoniya, nibwe na nennayi ni mabwe a ezhimiralida
nibwe na neetanu nahiwomihiwa ni mabwe a saridoniyu, nibwe na neetanu ni nimohi ni mabwe a saridiyu, nibwe na neetanu nabiili ni mabwe a kirisolitu, nibwe na neetanu nathaaru ni mabwe a berilu, nibwe na neetanu nennayi nahiwomihiwa ni mabwe a topaziyu, nibwe na neekumi ni mabwe a kirisoparasu, nibwe na neekumi ni nimohi ni mabwe a zhasintu, nibwe na neekumi ni meenddi ni mabwe a ametixta.
Milago kumi ni miinddi dhaali misanga dhoorameya kumi ni miinddi dhineeriwa perola, kadda mulago wasasanyiwa ni perola emohi yuulubale. Rampa a nluwa ndde aali a oro apamesesa, owooneyela wona viiduru.
Muluwani mule kagoonilemo nyuba ya Mulugu vowi muluwani mule nyuba ya Mulugu di Nabwiya Mulugu a Oowodha-wodha vamohi ni Nibila.
Nluwa ndde kamunarabuleleya nduwa naari mweeri wi dhimoneyegemo, vowi nthithimiho na Mulugu thinamoneyamo, panti ya nluwa ndde di Nibila.
Malogo enoodha yeeddege ni omoneya wula. Mamwene a elabo eneerege odhana muluwani mule nthithimiho neewa.
Milago ndo kadhidha dhifugiwaga vowi wewule kudha okalave mahiyu.
Nthithimiho ni nriiho na malogo maatene nneerege odhiiwana muluwani mule.
Mwihinje wa mahinje a egumi yoohumalaMungero ahigoonihaga mwihinje wa mahinje a egumi yoohumala yazherimelaga wona viiduru. Wakuma vampanddoni va Mulugu ni va Nibila.
Mwihinje ola wavira vaari va rampa a nluwa. Kadda seresere ya mwihinje ole vookala muthanko wa egumi yoohumala. Muthanko ole woovaha furuuta kumi ni biili dhoohiyana-hiyana, va kadda mweeri. Mataakuru a muthanko ole bowaayilihana athu a dhilabo.
Wule kudha okalave odduba. Mpanddo wa omwene wa Mulugu ni wa Nibila onaakale muluwani mwemule. Amwiimeleli aaye eneerege omwiimelela,
vano enoodha yoone kove yaaye, ndina naaye nnaakale vayuuji veewa.
Mahiyu kidha ekalawo. Kidha efunaga waara wa panti naari nduwa mwaha wi Nabwiya Mulugu dinakale waara weewa. Aliwa eneerege olamula okala ni okala.
Yesu onoodhaMungero ahigaaddelaga, wiira: “Madhu ala boororomeleya ni a ebaribari. Nabwiya, Mulugu a mineba dha anamavuhulela, ahimuruma mungero aaye wi awoonihe amwiimeleli aaye dhego dhinafuna opadduwa voohulogela”.
Yesu ahiwogaga, wiira: “Keeng'anani, ginoodha voohulogela. Ooreelihiwa baale enahariha madhu oovuhulela a niivuru ndda”.
Miyo, Zhuwawu, di miyo giiwile, goonile dhego dhedhi. Ngeewile, ngoonile dhego dhedhi gahikokora vamanyaloni vaaye wi gimweebedhe mungero agoonihile dhego dhedhi.
Mbwenye oliye ahigiirelaga: “Kawiire ndo! Miyo gili mwiimeleli ooligana ni we teto ni addibilo anamavuhulela, vamohi ni aatene eneewelela madhu a niivuru ndda. Vano omweebedhege Mulugu baahi”.
Teto ahiiraga: “Kwaalogohedhe madhu a ovuhulela a niivuru ndda vowi mudhidhi ohaaddamela.
Ole oneerana dhabure eeregenaave dhabure, ole oneetakaliha eeregenaave dhootakala, ole oli owogoowa eeregenaave dhowogoowa, ole oli oweela murima akalegeve oweela murima”.
Yesu ahiwogaga, wiira: “Keeng'anani, ginoodha voohulogela, ginoodhana yowaakeliha wi gimvahe kadda muthu mooligana ni mabasa aaye.
Miyo gili Alifa ni Omega, Muraaji ni Oomariha, Owambeela ni Oogomihedha”.
